OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778775073
OL,3,CIan Watkins death: Murder suspect told
OL,4,Cpolice 'prison is a dog-eat-dog world'
OL,6,FOne of the prisoners accused of
OL,7,Fmurdering Ian Watkins told police he
OL,8,Fdisposed of the knife used in the
OL,9,Ffatal stabbing because "prison is a
OL,10,Fdog-eat-dog world".
OL,12,FThe disgraced Lostprophets frontman
OL,13,Fwas serving 29 years for child sex
OL,14,Foffences when he was fatally attacked
OL,15,Fin his cell at HMP Wakefield on 11
OL,16,FOctober last year.
OL,18,FFellow prisoners Rico Gedel and Samuel
OL,19,FDodsworth deny murder and are on trial
OL,20,Fat Leeds Crown Court.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@RO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
