OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778775073
OL,3,CIan Watkins death: Murder suspect told
OL,4,Cpolice 'prison is a dog-eat-dog world'
OL,6,FThe court has heard Gedel stabbed
OL,7,FWatkins to death and Dodsworth helped
OL,8,Fhim by disposing of the knife
OL,9,Fafterwards.
OL,11,FProsecutors say both men are guilty of
OL,12,Fmurder because Gedel carried out the
OL,13,Fattack and Dodsworth knew it was going
OL,14,Fto happen and assisted him.
OL,16,FJurors heard that in his interview
OL,17,Fwith police, Dodsworth said he was not
OL,18,Finvolved in the attack and that Gedel
OL,19,Fpassed him the blade after walking out
OL,20,Fof Watkins' cell.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778775073
OL,3,CIan Watkins death: Murder suspect told
OL,4,Cpolice 'prison is a dog-eat-dog world'
OL,6,FDodsworth told officers he tried to
OL,7,Fgive the knife back to Gedel, but
OL,8,Fpanicked when he saw Watkins emerge
OL,9,Ffrom his cell with a large cut on his
OL,10,Fneck.
OL,12,FHe said he then wrapped the knife in
OL,13,Fsome tissue from his cell and threw it
OL,14,Fin a bin.
OL,16,FDodsworth told officers: "If you're a
OL,17,Fgrass, you're going to get cut up for
OL,18,Fit... when you're in prison you look
OL,19,Fafter yourself. Prison is a dog-eat-
OL,20,Fdog world in there and I have to put
OL,21,Fmy own safety first.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778775073
OL,3,CIan Watkins death: Murder suspect told
OL,4,Cpolice 'prison is a dog-eat-dog world'
OL,6,F"I panicked and wrapped it in a
OL,7,Ftissue, and saw the bin and threw it
OL,8,Fin."
OL,10,FDodsworth said he had never been
OL,11,Fviolent in prison, adding: "The only
OL,12,Fwrongdoing I've ever done is hurt a
OL,13,Fwoman, and that's it."
OL,15,FIn transcripts of the interview read
OL,16,Fin court, Dodsworth said he saw Gedel
OL,17,Flooking "suspicious" before the
OL,18,Fattack, and as if he was going to rob
OL,19,Fsomeone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@DO]sD@\OUuD@VO]yD@IOUyD@TO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778775073
OL,3,CIan Watkins death: Murder suspect told
OL,4,Cpolice 'prison is a dog-eat-dog world'
OL,6,FHe told police he wished he "had just
OL,7,Fmoved somewhere else" at that point,
OL,8,Fadding he was in the wrong place at
OL,9,Fthe wrong time.
OL,11,FAsked about whether he knew Watkins,
OL,12,FDodsworth said: "I know of him but
OL,13,Fhe's just another inmate to me which
OL,14,Fis just doing his time.
OL,16,F"I knew he were a famous person and he
OL,17,Fwas in for a sexual offence, but other
OL,18,Fthan that... I knew he would have been
OL,19,Fhigh profile, he would have had all
OL,20,Fthat money from fame."
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@UO]tD@QOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1778775073
OL,3,CIan Watkins death: Murder suspect told
OL,4,Cpolice 'prison is a dog-eat-dog world'
OL,6,FDodsworth said Watkins "didn't really
OL,7,Fmingle with lots of people" and there
OL,8,Fwas only one inmate whose cell he went
OL,9,Fin regularly.
OL,11,FDodsworth claimed he knew nothing
OL,12,Fabout threatening notes sent to
OL,13,FWatkins days before his death, but
OL,14,Fsaid: "I've known in the past Watkins
OL,15,Fhas had notes passed to him."
OL,17,FGedel and Dodsworth both deny murder
OL,18,Fand possession of a makeshift knife in
OL,19,Fprison.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@[O]vD@GOU
